				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">RTI does not increment the PC it pulls off the stack -- it differs from RTS in this regard.  Quoting the WDC docs for RTI:<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Unlike the RTS instruction, the program counter address pulled off the stack is the exact address to return to; the value on the stack is the value loaded into the program counter. It does not need to be incremented as a subroutine’s return address does.</div></div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

